description:
Once Upon a Time S03E00: Journey to Neverland 

Series co-creators Adam Horowitz and Edward Kitsis take us on a look back at highlights from Season 2, including Emma and Mary Margaret's time stranded in a different land and Rumplestiltskin's reunion with his son. Also: characters' backstories; and a preview of Season 3's adventure in Neverland.

This episode aired on CTV HD in Canada on September 28, 2013. Like all of my releases to date, the source is an analog rip, so the quality is, at best, something like A8 V8.
